<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Réservation confirmée</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: url('/images/cinema.gif') no-repeat center center fixed;
      background-size: cover;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 2rem;
    }
    
    .confirmation-card {
      background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 3rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }
    
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: #ffd700;
    }
    
    .confirmation-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: #4CAF50;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    
    .reservation-details {
      background-color: rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.1);
      border-left: 4px solid #ffd700;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      text-align: left;
    }
    
    .reservation-details p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
    }
    
    .reservation-details strong {
      color: #ffd700;
    }
    
    .btn {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background-color: #ffd700;
      color: #333;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0.5rem;
    }
    
    .btn:hover {
      background-color: #ffa500;
      color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-imprimer {
      background-color: #333;
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid #ffd700;
    }
    
    .btn-imprimer:hover {
      background-color: #444;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="confirmation-card">
    <div class="confirmation-icon">✓</div>
    <h1>Réservation confirmée !</h1>
    <p>Votre réservation a été enregistrée avec succès.</p>
    
    <div class="reservation-details">
      <p><strong>Film:</strong> <%= reservation.film.titre %></p>
      <p><strong>Date:</strong> <%= reservation.date_seance %></p>
      <p><strong>Heure:</strong> <%= reservation.heure_seance %></p>
      <p><strong>Salle:</strong> <%= reservation.salle.nom %></p>
      <p><strong>Places:</strong> <%= reservation.nb_places %> (<%= reservation.type_place %>)</p>
      <p><strong>Total:</strong> <%= reservation.montant %> €</p>
      <p><strong>Référence:</strong> <%= reservation.reference %></p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Un email de confirmation vous a été envoyé à l'adresse <%= user.email %>.</p>
    
    <div>
      <a href="/user/reservations" class="btn">Voir mes réservations</a>
      <a href="/user/queues" class="btn">Voir d'autres films</a>
      <button onclick="window.print()" class="btn btn-imprimer">Imprimer</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>